ActGarnishment, Attachment and Pension Diversion Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Garnishment and Attachment Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the GARNISHMENT AND ATTACHMENT REGULATIONS in order to ensure the Regulations are complete and accurate by providing the correct registry addresses and by allowing the Parliamentary Protective Service to use the prescribed method of response, which is currently available to other parliamentary entities.
